text: Frisco is a city in the Collin and Denton counties in Texas. It is in the area of Dallas-Fort Worth. The city is 25 miles north of Dallas Love Field and Dallas/Fort Worth International Airport. == History == Frisco was created in 1904. == Geography == Frisco has a total area of 69.19 square miles. == People == Frisco has 207,748 people living there. == References == == Other websites == Category:Cities in Collin County, Texas
title: Frisco, Texas
